Rebekah just had her 5th b-day on Dec.5. We had a party, but nothing
special. We mentioned that it was an extra- special birthday. My other
kids will have theirs on the 8th, 11th and 2 on the 18th (not twins) of
their birth months.
Mary-NY

Well, this is one celebration we had previously overlooked. Although, I do
vaguely remember making mention on Landons 12th birthday that he was 12 on
the 12th. Anna's is on the 23rd.. Ethans on the 18th ( He COULD celebrate
like Shryley, but he would have to be born on the 21st!) And JP's is on the
27th.. They will all be grown by the time thier star birthday comes around..
But it can still be fun

Teresa
